  "text": "The synchronization problem arises naturally in missions of surveillance or monitoring ( [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ), in structure assembly while the robots are loading and placing parts in a structure ( [CITATION_3] ), or even in the exploration process looking for parts to be assembled as performed in the ARCAS project (http://www.arcas-project.eu), to name but a few applications. In fact, its eventual solution may find many applications beyond the initial problems posed here.",
